<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_255_r1l17"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>w<ex>er</ex>nlein</expan> als du vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> haſt / wie dich <expan>ankome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſey . daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_255_r1l18">wır dır <expan>vnwıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>beweıſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_255_r1l19"><expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> dauon ʒemal niht . Denn daʒ vns ettlıch dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> den du </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_255_r1l20">ſchuldıg beleıbſt vaſt <expan>nachlawff<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd das Jr gern <expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan> . getrawn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_255_r1l21">wır dır wol . vnd ſehen ʒumal <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> . daʒ du dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> auſrıchteſt vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_255_r1l22">vnklaghaft macheſt / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan><ex>con</ex>u<ex>er</ex>ſıone</expan> Paulȷ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_255_r1l23">Von ~ dem Rate </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_255_r1l24">ʒu <expan>Nuremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_255" id="127v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Wernlein Rumel </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>W<ex>er</ex>nlein,</expan> als du uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hast, wie dich
                                <expan>ankome<ex>n</ex></expan> sey, daz wir dir
                                <expan>unwill<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>beweis<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        davon zemal niht, denn daz uns ettlich die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n,</expan>
                        den du schuldig beleibst, vast <expan>nachlawff<ex>en</ex></expan> und das
                        ir gern <expan>hett<ex>en</ex></expan>; getrawn wir dir wol und sehen zumal
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, daz du die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ausrichtest und unklaghaft machest.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan><ex>con</ex>v<ex>er</ex>sione</expan> Pauli. <lb/>Von dem rate zu
                                <expan>Nuremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan></ab>
</div>
